summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use, amending Plat 43E, page 115, Plat 44W, page 116, Plat 50E, page 129, and Plat 51W, page 130 of the Official Land Use Map Seattle Municipal Code Section 23.32.016, to rezone property generally bounded by Alaskan Way South, Railroad Way South, First Avenue South, South Royal Brougham Way, Fourth Avenue South, South Holgate Street, and Utah Avenue South, and implementing a rezone recommendation of the Greater Duwamish Manufacturing/Industrial Center Plan.
